# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Clan jump squads field squad-strength jump-capable warriors for reconnaissance and vertical-access missions. Smaller than a standard Clan jump Point, these formations operate as observation teams, rooftop security elements, and insertion forces where reduced numbers and three-dimensional mobility compensate for limited sustained firepower. Their compact size makes them easier to deploy from limited transport assets.</p>
</overview>

